Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - User' out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - User' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Wait - User' occurrences across all cases

Name: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - User' compared to the frequency of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: Percentage of 'Accepted + Wait - User' out of all 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Metric: Number of 'Accepted + Wait - User' activities

Name: Frequency of 'Accepted + Wait - User' appearing in variants that do not contain 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average number of activities occurring between 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the next 'Completed + Resolved' activity
